what_worked: Applied prefetch_fact_join, single_pass_aggregation: Decorrelated EXISTS subqueries by creating CTEs for filtered dates and each sales channel, then used INTERSECT and UNION to enforce the complex existence logic before joining with customer dimensions.
why_it_worked: Pre-joining filtered dimensions with fact table before aggregation reduces join input; Consolidating repeated scans into CASE aggregates reduces I/O from N scans to 1
